0each%20have%20to%20make%20that%20personal%20choice%20together.%20This%20can%20be%20as%20complicated%20as%20it%20sounds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnyone%20who%20cares%20enough%20to%20consider%20the%20consequences%2C%20their%20own%20abilities%2C%20and%20all%20the%20realities%20of%20parenthood%20may%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20know%20if%20or%20when%20they%20should%20have%20children.%20However%2C%20where%20those%20considerations%20take%20a%20person%20varies%20by%20the%20individual.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20people%20aren't%20comfortable%20having%20kids%20until%20they%20have%20four%20years%20of%20tuition%20and%20a%20wedding%20fund%20set%20aside%20in%20a%20dedicated%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esavings%20account%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Others%20are%20comfortable%20starting%20a%20family%20as%20long%20as%20they%20make%20enough%20to%20afford%20diapers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20some%20can't%20imagine%20bringing%20a%20child%20into%20the%20world%20at%20all.%20Again%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20have%20children%20or%20not%20is%20much%20too%20personal%20for%20there%20to%20ever%20be%20one%20right%20answer.%20The%20trouble%20is%2C%20however%2C%20exactly%20what%20you're%20experiencing%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%2C%20the%20right%20answer%20for%20one%20half%20of%20a%20couple%20is%20very%20different%20than%20it%20is%20for%20the%20other%20half.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20you%20do%20anything%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20are%20clear%20on%20what%20your%20husband%20is%20really%20saying.%20He's%20either%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20kids.%20Besides%2C%20they're%20too%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20he's%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20we%20could%20have%20kids%3B%20too%20bad%20we%20can't%20afford%20them.%26quot%3B%20If%20it's%20the%20former%2C%20and%20he%20doesn't%20actually%20want%20to%20be%20a%20father%2C%20you%20must%20handle%20things%20much%20differently%20than%20if%20he%20really%20wants%20children%20but%20finds%20the%20price%20tag%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnfortunately%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20have%20kids%20but%20your%20husband%20simply%20doesn't%2C%20you%20have%20a%20tough%20decision%20to%20make.%20You%20can%20try%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20his%20core%20objections%20and%20attempt%20to%20change%20his%20mind%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20bet%20on%20your%20success.%20Even%20if%20you%20manage%20to%20get%20your%20way%2C%20you%20may%20find%20yourself%20living%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20his%20resentment%20and%20regret%20over%20not%20living%20out%20his%20child-free%20dreams.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou're%20better%20off%20accepting%20his%20stance%20and%20figuring%20out%20your%20own.%20What%20do%20you%20want%20more%3A%20your%20husband%20or%20future%20children%3F%20Remember%2C%20there%20is%20no%20right%20answer%2C%20only%20your%20answer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20are%20sure%20that%20your%20husband%20does%20want%20children%20on%20some%20level%20and%20the%20cost%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20holding%20him%20back%2C%20I%20think%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20ways%20you%20might%20get%20him%20past%20the%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETry%20looking%20for%20trusted%20friends%20who%20you%20suspect%20aren't%20rolling%20in%20cash%20but%20still%20have%20kids.%20Explain%20your%20dilemma%20to%20them%2C%20and%20then%20ask%20your%20husband%20if%20he%20would%20be%20open%20to%20having%20dinner%20with%20these%20friends%20and%20discussing%20the%20financial%20impact%20parenthood%20has%20had%20on%20them%20and%20the%20emotional%20satisfaction%20that%20it's%20brought.%20Ask%20them%20if%20having%20their%20kids%20was%20worth%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20our%20first%20child%20a%20year%20after%20we%20married%20%E2%80%94%20four%20years%20earlier%20than%20planned.%20This%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20my%20career%2C%20as%20my%20earning%20power%20at%20the%20time%20wouldn't%20have%20come%20close%20to%20covering%20the%20cost%20of%20childcare.%20We%20always%20wanted%20our%20children%20spaced%20closely%20in%20age%2C%20so%20we%20went%20ahead%20and%20had%20two%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20start%2C%20our%20budget%20has%20revolved%20around%20diapers%2C%20car%20seats%2C%20preschool%20tuition%2C%20and%20massive%20grocery%20hauls.%20Our%20three%20children%20defined%20our%20entire%20financial%20history.%20I%20know%20I%20can%20speak%20for%20my%20husband%20when%20I%20say%20%3Cem%3Ewe%20wouldn't%20change%20a%20thing%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20new%20car%20or%20home%20purchase%20we've%20made%20to%20accommodate%20our%20growing%20family%2C%20every%20time%20we've%20had%20to%20multiply%20airline%20tickets%20by%20five%2C%20every%20single%20penny%20has%20been%20worth%20it.%20Yes%2C%20this%20means%20we've%20had%20to%20raise%20our%20kids%20in%20a%20way%20that%20will%20best%20qualify%20them%20for%20scholarships.%20All%20our%20vacations%20have%20been%20domestic%20rather%20than%20foreign.%20It%20has%20meant%20a%20million%20and%20one%20financial%20sacrifices%2C%20and%20still%20%E2%80%A6%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20because%20this%20has%20been%20the%20case%20for%20us%2C%20however%2C%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20will%20be%20for%20everyone%20else.%20My%20experience%20tells%20me%20your%20instinct%20that%20%26quot%3Braising%20a%20child%20is%20more%20than%20a%20price%20tag%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20good%20one%2C%20though.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20your%20husband%20is%20open%20to%20hearing%20this%2C%20you%20could%20also%20get%20down%20to%20the%20specifics%20of%20that%20price%20tag.%20Put%20a%20realistic%20mock%20budget%20together%20that%20reflects%20the%20sacrifices%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20make%20and%20those%20you%20aren't.%20Perhaps%20showing%20him%20that%20a%20working%20strategy%20exists%20will%20give%20him%20the%20confidence%20to%20go%20for%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20even%20if%20he%20doesn't%2C%20remember%20that%20staying%20honest%20is%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20right%20now.%20You%20want%20to%20be%20a%20mother.%20You're%20allowed%20to%20want%20this%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20your%20husband's%20dire%20calculations%2C%20it%20feels%20unwise%3B%20even%20if%20your%20husband%20doesn't%20feel%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShoving%20your%20desire%20for%20a%20child%20down%20will%20only%20cause%20your%20husband%20to%20live%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20your%20regret%20and%20resentment%2C%20which%20is%20as%20unfair%20to%20him%20as%20it%20would%20be%20to%20you.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20keep%20your%20heart%20open%2C%20make%20your%20case%2C%20and%20make%20the%20right%20decisions%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20hard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffin