C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmma%20Le%20Teace%20said%20select%20cabins%20and%20itineraries%20could%20make%20you%20more%20prone%20to%20seasickness.%3Cp%3EEmma%20Le%20Teace%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELa%20Teace%20has%20been%20on%20more%20cruises%20than%20most%20people%20will%20in%20a%20lifetime.%20Yet%2C%20she's%20only%20been%20seasick%20about%20five%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20tip%3F%20Avoid%20itineraries%20like%20an%20Arctic%20Circle%20or%20transatlantic%20sailing%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20when%20(and%20where)%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20encounter%20a%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20consider%20a%20mid-ship%2C%20lower-deck%20cabin.%20And%20if%20you%20do%20feel%20queasy%2C%20avoid%20indulging%20in%20your%20drinks%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20Still%20set%20on%20that%20Arctic%20cruise%3F%20Consider%20a%20little-known%20ferry%20company.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Havila%20Polaris%20sailing%20past%20land%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ddbed9b8b41a9673fb699e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmma%20La%20Teace%20said%20her%20Havila%20Voyages%20ferry%20was%20as%20nice%20as%20a%20conventional%20cruise.%3Cp%3EHavila%20Voyages%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20La%20Teace%20spent%2012%20days%20cruising%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%20and%20Norway%20with%20Havila%20Voyages%2C%20a%20Norwegian%20ferry%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20ocean%20cruises%2C%20which%20often%20spend%20a%20day%20at%20one%20destination%2C%20the%20ferry%20stopped%20at%20up%20to%20seven%20ports%20daily%2C%20lingering%20between%2020%20minutes%20to%20two%20hours%20at%20each%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20much%20prefer%20to%20have%20lots%20of%20little%20ports%20a%20day%20rather%20than%20one%20really%20long%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20La%20Teace%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20put%20on%20my%20coat%20and%20snow%20boots%2C%20run%20outside%2C%20have%20a%20look%20at%20the%20town%2C%20and%20come%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20onboard%20entertainment%20or%20traditional%20theater.%20Still%2C%20she%20had%20plenty%20of%20fun%2C%20and%20the%20food%20and%20cabin%20were%20surprisingly%20comparable%20to%20those%20of%20a%20conventional%20cruise%20liner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20every%20bit%20as%20nice%20as%20a%20cruise%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20most%20people%20would%20like%20that%20if%20they%20did%20cruising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Pro%20tip%3A%20La%20Teace%20said%20if%20you%20like%20Alaska%20voyages%2C%20you'll%20likely%20enjoy%20Norway%2C%20too.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20you%20prefer%20beachy%20Caribbean%20cruises%2C%20you'll%20likely%20appreciate%20Mediterranean%20and%20Canary%20Islands%20itineraries.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20Consider%20when%20a%20balcony%20cabin%20(virtual%20or%20not)%20is%20worth%20the%20cost.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emma%20Le%20Teace%20standing%20on%20cruise%20balcony%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ddbb67b8b41a9673fb68c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmma%20Le%20Teace%20is%20more%20inclined%20to%20book%20a%20balcony%20cabin%20for%20an%20exciting%20itinerary%20far%20from%20home%20in%20the%20UK.%3Cp%3EEmma%20Le%20Teace%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20budget%20cruiser%2C%20Le%20Teace%20frequently%20opts%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-getting-booted-from-overbooked-cruise-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bguaranteed%26quot%3B%20inside%20cabins%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20exciting%20the%20itinerary%2C%20and%20the%20further%20she%20is%20from%20home%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20she%20will%20splurge%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-wonder-vs-icon-of-the-seas-balcony-cabin-compared-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebalcony%20cabin%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20going%20to%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Alaska%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20I%20want%20to%20see%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20same%20can't%20be%20said%20for%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20%26quot%3Bvirtual%20balcony%26quot%3B%20cabins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20these%20accommodations%20have%20a%20large%20digital%20screen%20that%20displays%20a%20live%20view%20of%20the%20ship's%20exterior%2C%20akin%20to%20a%20real%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20Le%20Teace%20said%20it%20was%20confusing%3A%20The%20screen%20was%20on%20the%20wrong%20wall%20and%20showed%20the%20view%20from%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20it%20helpful%20to%20check%20the%20weather%3F%20Yes.%20Was%20it%20nice%20to%20see%20the%20birds%20flying%20by%3F%20Yes.%20However%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20didn't%20convince%20me%20in%20any%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20go%20out%20of%20her%20way%20for%20it%20again.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20like%2C%20pull%20the%20curtains%2C%20and%20your%20brain's%20going%20to%20think%20that's%20a%20window.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E4.%20If%20you're%20seeking%20a%20quiet%20space%2C%20go%20to%20a%20bar%20that%20isn't%20open%20yet.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22empty%20bar%20on%20Carnival%20Firenze%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668c4351098114dafd1a6ceb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELounge%20at%20a%20bar%20that%20isn't%20open%20yet%20to%20avoid%20big%20crowds.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELe%20Teace%20prefers%20avoiding%20big%20crowds%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20that%20means%20swimming%20on%20a%20rainy%20day%20when%20everyone%20else%20is%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20the%20same%2C%20she%20suggests%20spending%20your%20afternoon%20at%20a%20bar%20that%20doesn't%20open%20until%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20order%20drinks%2C%20but%20the%20lounge%20seating%20will%20still%20be%20there.%20Plus%2C%20you%20can%20always%20bring%20beverages%20from%20another%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E5.%20Avoid%20the%20dinner%20rush%20by%20eating%20when%20the%20main%20dining%20room%20opens.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plate%20of%20prime%20rib%20with%20mashed%20potatoes%20on%20UTopia%20of%20the%20Seas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67576b8152dd0818d1a617b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20dinner%20in%20the%20main%20dining%20room%2C%20consider%20eating%20when%20it%20opens%20to%20avoid%20long%20lines%20during%20peak%20times.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cruise%20expert%20eats%20her%20main%20dining%20room%20dinner%20at%205%20p.m.%2C%20when%20many%20open%2C%20to%20avoid%20long%20lines%20during%20peak%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20always%20stop%20by%20the%20buffet%20later%20at%20night%20if%20you're%20feeling%20peckish.%20(She's%20especially%20partial%20to%20Celebrity's%2C%20which%20she%20said%20is%20often%20stocked%20with%20fresh%20vegetables%20and%20fruit.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E6.%20Shoulder%20season%20sailings%20can%20be%20a%20good%20bang%20for%20your%20buck.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225313%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cruise%20near%20port%20of%20Palma%20in%20Mallorca%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ddc0f069253ccddf9a0390%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223985%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShoulder%20season%20cruises%20have%20below-peak%20fares%20and%20decent%20weather.%3Cp%3EClara%20Margais%2Fpicture%20allian