E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9e33957-3800-44c2-8cd4-9229273c2fd8%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20growth%20welcomed%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBedford%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20Snowmass%20in%201968%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021%2C%20said%20it%20was%20all%20about%20%26quot%3Bsex%2C%20drugs%2C%20and%20rock%20'n'%20roll%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201971%2C%20the%20Eagles%20were%20performing%20in%20small%20Aspen%20clubs.%20The%20singer%20John%20Denver%20had%20moved%20to%20Aspen%20and%20became%20a%20family%20friend.%20Winters%20were%20filled%20with%20skiing%20powder%20days%2C%20and%20summers%20were%20spent%20playing%20softball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAspen%20was%20known%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20Snowmass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGod%2C%20Snowmass%20was%20so%20small%2C%26quot%3B%20Bedford%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20was%20so%20tight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20locals%2C%20that%20unfamiliarity%20was%20a%20plus.%20It%20meant%20cheaper%20lift%20tickets%2C%20little%20traffic%2C%20and%20lower%20real-estate%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mel%20Blumenthal%20first%20visited%20Snowmass%20about%2035%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20area%20had%20%26quot%3Bsmall-town%20charm.%26quot%3B%20Now%2C%20he%20fears%20that%20charm%20is%20fading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlumenthal%2C%20who%20splits%20his%20time%20between%20Snowmass%20and%20Santa%20Monica%2C%20California%2C%20initially%20supported%20the%20plans%20for%20Base%20Village.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20beginning%2C%20I%20was%20convinced%20it%20was%20necessary%20in%20order%20to%20economically%20compete%20as%20a%20resort%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20started%20to%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20project%20as%20it%20changed%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20living%20across%20the%20street%2C%20he%20rarely%20visits%20the%20area%20and%20said%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20trend%20among%20residents.%20He's%20also%20concerned%20about%20how%20Snowmass%20will%20balance