20important%20thing%20for%20us%20to%20do'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Curtin%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20DC%20Central%20Kitchen%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nonprofit%20aimed%20at%20combating%20hunger%20that%20operates%20caf%C3%A9s%20throughout%20DC%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20he%20recognizes%20how%20important%20federal%20workers%20are%20to%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20wildly%20important%20part%20of%20our%20local%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Curtin%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20DC%20has%20survived%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20other%20economic%20turmoil%20that%20other%20parts%20of%20our%20country%20have%20not.%20And%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20take%20that%20for%20granted.%20We%20value%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20February%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwjla.com%2Fresources%2Fpdf%2Fcad762a5-3012-4db7-abf2-c1ead1ab2409-February2025RevenueEstimateLetter.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20DC's%20chief%20financial%20office%20said%20that%20about%20190%2C000%20federal%20employees%20work%20in%20DC%2C%20which%20is%20about%2025%25%20of%20DC's%20total%20jobs.%20Administration%20officials%20said%20that%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-doge-terminations-reinstatements-legal-battle-maryland-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E25%2C000%20federal%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20terminated%20across%20all%20agencies%2C%20though%20that%20total%20is%20spread%20out%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurtin%20said%20that%20DC%20Central%20Kitchen%20is%20offering%20federal%20workers%2050%25%20off%20of%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%20purchase%20at%20one%20of%20the%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20which%20he%20said%20he%20hopes%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20great%20way%20to%20welcome%20that%20particular%20part%20of%20our%20community%20who%20is%20now%20facing%20unanticipated%20and%20unnecessary%20obstacles%20and%20hurdles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20looking%20at%20using%20food%20in%20a%20bigger%20way%20than%20just%20simply%20feeding%20people%2C%20and%20saying%20that%20food%20has%20the%20power%20to%20bring%20people%20together%2C%20to%20unite%20people%2C%20to%20bring%20comfort%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20important%20thing%20for%20us%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DC%20Central%20Kitchen%20discount%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dc5e74b8b41a9673fb423f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDC%20Central%20Kitchen's%20discount%20sign%20for%20federal%20workers.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lincoln%20Barbour%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETina%20Latimer%2C%20a%20manager%20at%20exercise%20studio%20DC%20Row%2C%20said%20that%20when%20the%20studio%20saw%20how%20federal%20workers%20were%20being%20affected%20by%20Trump's%20changes%20to%20the%20workforce%2C%20DC%20Row%20started%20offering%20free%20classes.%20The%20offer%20will%20continue%20%26quot%3Bas%20long%20as%20it's%20needed.%26quot%3B%20The%20new%20member%20offer%20is%20typically%20%2435%20for%20two%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20a%20ping%20pong%20kind%20of%20a%20situation%20where%20people%20are%20being%20let%20go%2C%20but%20then%20they're%20being%20brought%20back%2C%20but%20then%20there's%20also%20a%20period%20of%20shock%20and%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20their%20next%20steps%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Latimer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELatimer%20was%20referring%20to%20recent%20court%20orders%20requiring%20federal%20agencies%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-orders-trump-reinstate-fired-probationary-federal-workers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereinstate%20thousands%20of%20the%20probationary%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20had%20previously%20terminated.%20Some%20reinstated%20federal%20workers%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20back-and-forth%20nature%20of%20their%20employment%20has%20left%20them%20in%20a%20limbo%20state%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20confident%20they'll%20be%20able%20to%20retain%20their%20jobs%20once%20they're%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20exercise%20classes%20free%20of%20charge%2C%20Latimer%20said%20she%20hopes%20it'll%20give%20federal%20workers%20%26quot%3Ba%20kind%20of%20a%20therapy%20and%20mental%20clarity%2C%20clearing%20out%20your%20mind%2C%20but%20also%20getting%20a%20physical%20workout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20vet%20clinics%20are%20also%20stepping%20in.%20Allison%20Gross%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20at%20Union%20Veterinary%20Clinic%20in%20DC%2C%20said%20that%20being%20located%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20clinic's%20clients%20are%20federal%20workers.%20The%20clinic%20decided%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20one%20stress%20off%20of%20people's%20minds%26quot%3B%20by%20offering%20a%20free%20exam%20for%20their%20pets%2C%20she%20said.%20Wellness%20exams%20can%20typically%20run%20from%20%2450%20to%20%24150%2C%20dependent%20on%20the%20pet's%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDC%20is%20a%20transient%20area.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20here%20without%20a%20lot%20of%20family%20or%20support%20system%2C%20and%20they%20come%20home%20to%20their%20cat%20or%20their%20dog%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Gross%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20add%20any%20extra%20stress%20to%20their%20lives%20if%20they're%20worried%20that%20their%20companion%20is%20sick%20or%20even%20just%20needs%20their%20routine%20wellness%20care.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20the%20Trump%20administration%20has%20in%20store%20for%20federal%20workers%20next.%20The%20Office%20of%20Personnel%20Management%20asked%20federal%20agencies%20to%20prepare%20reorganization%20plans%2C%20and%20some%20have%20started%20implementing%20those%20plans%20through%20return-to-office%20mandates%20and%20reductions%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20ongoing%20uncertainty%2C%20DC%20Row's%20Latimer%20said%20that%20businesses%20in%20the%20nation's%20capitol%20should%20view%20it%20as%20their%20responsibility%20to%20support%20a%20major%20part%20of%20their%20customer%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20for%20businesses%20because%20each%20of%20us%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20community%2C%20we%20feed%20off%20of%20each%20other%2C%20and%20if%20we're%20not%20there%20to%20support%20the%20community%2C%20then%20why%20would%20we%20expect%20the%20community%20to%20support%20us%3F%26quot%3B%20Latimer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%20or%20story%20to%20share%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97%20or%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-trump-dc-businesses-offereing-deals-discounts-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742723101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dc453469253ccddf99d5ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-workers-trump-dc-businesses-offereing-deals-discounts-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20range%20of%20businesses%20in%20the%20nation's%20capitol%20are%20rallying%20behind%20federal%20wo