e%20J.Crew%20and%20Madewell%20are%20good%20places%20to%20start%20looking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20got%20your%20base%20outfit%2C%20here's%20what%20Ferguson%20recommends%20to%20switch%20seamlessly%20from%20the%20office%20to%20the%20afterparty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224efba84f-31c8-4082-a8c3-939bbffbb4b4%5C%22%3EPlan%20ahead%20and%20dress%20comfortably%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStaying%20out%20after%20an%20eight-hour%20shift%20requires%20some%20comfort%2C%20Ferguson%20said.%20From%20the%20morning%20commute%20to%20bustling%20nightlife%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20long%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20after-work%20plans%20are%20spontaneous%2C%20but%20Ferguson%20said%20it's%20good%20to%20plan%20ahead.%20If%20you%20know%20the%20venue%20you%20plan%20to%20visit%20after%20work%2C%20it%20makes%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20%26quot%3Bdress%20appropriately%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20block%20heels%20would%20be%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%2C%20those%20who%20can't%20tolerate%20their%20achy%20work%20shoes%20should%20plan%20to%20swap%20them%20out%2C%20the%20stylist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22715ae19e-4865-40f0-9f27-e190c8636fef%5C%22%3EDon't%20shy%20away%20from%20shedding%20layers%20and%20adding%20accessories%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20blazers%20and%20sweater%20vests%20make%20your%20outfit%20more%20corporate%2C%20layer%20them%20over%20a%20shirt%20(perhaps%20a%20polo)%20and%20take%20them%20off%20for%20a%20more%20casual%20look%20after%20work.%20Or%2C%20roll%20up%20the%20sleeves%20of%20your%20blazer%20and%20flip%20the%20collar%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20your%20socks%20off%20and%20put%20your%20shoes%20back%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Ferguson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20suggested%20adding%20%26quot%3Bstatement%26quot%3B%20jewelry%20or%20a%20watch%20can%20elevate%20your%20daily%20attire%20and%20make%20it%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Bpencil%20skirt%20and%20a%20plain%20blouse%2