0family%2C%20providing%20necessary%20support%20to%20them.%20We%20are%20also%20actively%20coordinating%20with%20authorities%20in%20both%20countries%20and%20adhering%20to%20the%20due%20process.%20Ensuring%20the%20wellbeing%20of%20our%20colleague%20is%20our%20top%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Tech%20Mahindra%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742720580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fkostv8ko_indian-techie-at-doha_625x300_23_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famit-gupta-tech-mahindra-techie-detained-in-qatar-gujarat-familys-long-wait-after-indian-techie-working-in-qatar-detained-7990683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amit%20Gupta%2C%20the%20country%20head%20of%20IT%20giant%20Tech%20Mahindra%20in%20Qatar%2C%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Gulf%20country's%20State%20Security%20on%20January%201%20and%20has%20been%20in%20detention%20for%20the%20past%20three%20months%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20cash%20row%3A%20Burnt%20Rs%20500%20notes%20'found'%20near%20Justice%20Varma's%20house%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742720431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119372684%2Cimgsize-973478.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fjudge-cash-row-burnt-pieces-of-rs-500-notes-found-near-justice-yashwant-varmas-residence%2Farticleshow%2F119372521.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fjudge-cash-row-burnt-pieces-of-rs-500-notes-found-near-justice-yashwant-varmas-residence%2Farticleshow%2F119372521.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20Adolescence%3A%20Are%20You%20A%20'Docile%20Body'%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGood%20storytelling%20engages%2C%20but%20great%20storytelling%20enthralls.%20It%20doesn't%20simply%20entertain%3B%20it%20disarms%2C%20deceives%2C%20and%20leaves%20you%20spellbound%2C%20say%2C%20like%20the%20illusion%20of%20a%20veteran%20magician.%20You%20see%20the%20trick%20unfold%2C%20yet%20surrender%20willingly%2C%20captivated%20by%20the%20craft.%20That's%20the%20triumph%20of%20the%20pilot%20episode%20of%20%3Cem%3EAdolescence%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20British%20crime%20drama%20miniseries%20that%20has%20emerged%20as%20an%20unexpected%20spring%20blockbuster%20for%20Netflix.%20Everyone%20seems%20to%20be%20talking%20about%20it%2C%20everyone%20seems%20to%20be%20moved%20by%20its%20gut-wrenching%20realism.%20%E2%80%9CA%20technical%20masterclass%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20say%2C%20marveling%20at%20the%20audacity%20of%20an%20entire%20series%20captured%20in%20a%20single%2C%20continuous%20take.%20And%20then%2C%20there's%20the%20inevitable%20refrain%E2%80%94%E2%80%9CThat%20third%20episode%3F%20Peak%20television.%E2%80%9D%20They're%20right.%20That%20third%20episode%20is%20a%20narrative%20feat%20(and%20we'll%20get%20there%20soon).%20But%20for%20now%2C%20let's%20talk%20about%20the%20opening%20hour.%20That%20first%2C%20searing%20plunge%20into%20a%20world%20that%20grips%20you%20by%20the%20collar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Noose%20Tightens%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20early%20morning.%20DI%20Luke%20Bascombe%20(Ashley%20Walters)%20and%20his%20team%20raid%20a%20house.%20They%20move%20with%20practised%20urgency.%20They%20are%20many.%20Armed%2C%20deliberate%2C%20prepared%20for%20the%20worst.%20The%20house%20is%20torn%20apart%2C%20every%20corner%20overturned.%20You%20assume%20they're%20after%20a%20fugitive%2C%20someone%20dangerous%2C%20someone%20capable%20of%20unspeakable%20harm.%20But%20then%20comes%20the%20shock.%20They're%20here%20for%20a%20boy.%20Jamie%20(Owen%20Cooper)%2C%2013%20years%20old%2C%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20murder.%20The%20sight%20unsettles.%20You%20want%20to%20pause%2C%20to%20question.%20But%20the%20moment%20doesn't%20wait.%20Jamie%20crumbles%20as%20they%20lead%20him%20away.%20At%20the%20station%2C%20the%20machinery%20grinds%20on.%20Procedural%20questions.%20Strip%20searches.%20Blood%20samples.%20The%20sterile%20hum%20of%20officialdom.%20A%20chilling%20interrogation.%20And%20then%20it's%20revealed%3A%20he%20really%20did%20it.%20Jamie%2C%20just%2013%2C%20is%20here%20for%20a%20reason.%20He's%20not%20a%20victim%20of%20some%20mistake%20or%20misunderstanding.%20He%20stabbed%20someone.%20Took%20a%20life.%20The%20words%20land%20heavily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20simply%20the%20opening%20of%20a%20show.%20It%20is%20the%20tightening%20of%20a%20noose.%20But%20while%20the%20revelation%20is%20startling%2C%20what%20truly%20unsettled%20me%20was%20something%20else%20entirely.%20The%20cold%2C%20mechanical%20rhythm%20of%20the%20characters'%20lives.%20Throughout%20the%20first%20episode%2C%20the%20way%20they%20speak%2C%20the%20way%20they%20move%2C%20every%20gesture%20feels%20calculated.%20Even%20in%20the%20face%20of%20brutality%2C%20there%20is%20no%20rupture%3B%20only%20the%20sterile%20hum%20of%20procedure.%20It's%20as%20if%20discipline%20has%20seeped%20into%20their%20very%20mannerisms.%20It's%20as%20if%20the%20supposed%20politeness%20isn't%20kindness%3B%20it's%20a%20polished%20form%20of%20control.%20Bascombe%2C%20his%20colleagues%2C%20the%20local%20solicitor%2C%20the%20sergeants%2C%20the%20nurse%E2%80%94all%20operate%20like%20cogs%20in%20a%20machine.%20Their%20words%20are%20measured%2C%20their%20actions%20devoid%20of%20warmth.%20%C2%A0Even%20care%2C%20when%20offered%2C%20feels%20like%20protocol.%20There's%20really%20only%20the%20numbing%20precision%20of%20a%20system%20that%20demands%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F99vgpbc_adolescence-_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20watching%20all%20of%20this%2C%20what%20struck%20me%20most%20was%20how%20these%20people%20had%20become%20docile%20bodies.%20A%20term%20coined%20by%20French%20philosopher%20Michel%20Foucault%20in%20his%20seminal%20work%20%3Cem%3EDiscipline%20and%20Punish%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20spoke%20of%20individuals%20molded%20by%20the%20quiet%20machinery%20of%20control%2C%20shaped%20into%20submission%20through%20the%20subtleties%20of%20discipline%20and%20surveillance.%20In%20modern%20societies%2C%20Foucault%20argued%2C%20power%20rarely%20announces%20itself%20with%20force.%20Instead%2C%20it%20seeps%20into%20the%20everyday%3A%20through%20routines%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20the%20omnipresent%20gaze%20of%20authority.%20It%20demands%20not%20only%20obedience%20but%20internalisation.%20After%20all%2C%20then%20the%20body%20becomes%20a%20vessel%20of%20compliance%2C%20its%20movements%20measured%2C%20its%20desires%20restrained.%20Here%2C%20too%2C%20the%20characters%20are%20not%20simply%20participants%20in%20a%20system%3B%20they%20are%20its%20products.%20Their%20behaviour%2C%20their%20speech%2C%20even%20their%20notions%20of%20care%2C%20are%20dictated%20by%20the%20very%20structures%20that%20claim%20to%20uphold%20order.%20What%20remains%20is%20a%20hollowed-out%20humanity%2C%20where%20conformity%20is%20not%20just%20expected%20but%20inevitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenging%20Foucalt%20Himself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20the%20episode%20ends%2C%20this%20reading%20feels%20almost%20trivial%3A%20a%20passing%20thought%2C%20an%20unnecessary%20subtextual%20implication.%20The%20show%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20isn't%20primarily%20concerned%20with%20Foucault's%20complex%20notions.%20It%20is%20far%20too%20preoccupied%20with%20its%20own%20urgencies%20to%20dwell%20on%20the%20mechanics%20of%20docility.%20But%20then%2C%20it%20startles%20once%20more.%20In%20the%20episodes%20that%20follow%2C%20it%20keeps%20circling%20back%20to%20those%20very%20ideas.%20Each%20time%20in%20a%20different%20setting%2C%20with%20heightened%20stakes%2C%20sharper%20conflicts%2C%20and%20more%20layered%20resolutions.%20It's%20as%20if%20the%20show%20refuses%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20question%2C%20bending%20it%20to%20its%20will.%20It's%20as%20though%20the%20show%20urges%20us%20to%20chase%20the%20answers%2C%20daring%20us%20to%20plunge%20headlong%20into%20the%20unknown.%20And%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20doesn't%20merely%20echo%20Foucault%3B%20it%20sometimes%20challenges%20him.%20It%20bends%20his%20theories%2C%20reshapes%20them%2C%20and%20casts%20them%20into%20the%20fractured%20mirror%20of%20contemporary%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20first%20episode%20subtly%20explored%20the%20subjugation%20within%20the%20walls%20of%20a%20police%20station%2C%20the%20second%20shifts%20its%20gaze%20to%20a%20school.%20A%20space%20where%20docile%20bodies%20are%20not%20just%20maintained%20but%20conscientiously%20crafted.%20However%2C%20unlike%20the%20rigid%20confines%20of%20the%20station%2C%20the%20school%20is%20all%20about%20chaos.%20Here%2C%20Bascombe%20and%20DS%20Misha%20Frank%20(Faye%20Marsay)%20arrive%20seeking%20answers%2C%20yet%20find%20themselves%20confronted%20by%20something%20far%20more%20unsettling.%20Teachers%20wear%20their%20anxieties%20like%20second%20skins%2C%20students%20roam%20unchecked%2C%20smartphones%20capture%20every%20moment%2C%20and%20bullying%20thrives%20openly.%20The%20questions%20about%20the%20murder%20are%20met%20with%20ridicule.%20The%20students%20mock%2C%20dismiss%2C%20and%20toy%20with%20the%20detectives'%20authority.%20This%20is%20no%20orderly%20institution.%20The%20children%20are%20not%20the%20obedient%20figures%20Foucault%20spoke%20of%E2%80%94not%20yet%2C%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiscipline%20Is%20Control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20things%20suddenly%20change.%20A%20false%20fire%20alarm%20is%20heard%2C%20and%2C%20in%20an%20instant%2C%20discipline%20materialises.%20Without%20force%2C%20without%20resistance%2C%20bodies%20fall%20in%20line.%20The%20unruly%20become%20compliant.%20They%20are%20led%20to%20the%20grounds%2C%20organised%20into%20rows.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20Foucault's%20theories%20breathe%20afresh.%20Schools%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20are%20sites%20of%20regulation%20and%20subversion.%20Places%20where%20control%20is%20enforced%20not%20through%20visible%20chains%2C%20but%20through%20routine.%20The%20simple%20acts%20of%20standing%20in%20line%2C%20sitting%20still%2C%20or%20rehearsing%20drills%20are%20no%20accidents.%20They%20are%20rehearsals%20of%20obedience%2C%20performances%20of%20submission.%20And%20just%20like%20that%2C%20the%20illusion%20of%20chaos%20is%20shattered%2C%20revealing%20the%20order%20that%20was%20always%20waiting%20beneath.%20Much%20like%20the%20show's%20fixation%20with%20docility%2C%20which%20very%20much%20stays%20beneath%20the%20surface%2C%20until%20the%20third%20episode%20brings%20it%20surging%20forth.%20No%20longer%20subtle%2C%20no%20longer%20concealed%2C%20as%20if%20it%20had%20only%20been%20waiting%20to%20be%20seen.%20In%20fact%2C%20you%20barely%20notice%20when%20it%20shifts%20from%20the%20periphery%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20show's%20central%20thematic%20foundations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F9a1sgei8_adolescence-_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20first%20episode%20was%20about%20who%20did%20it%2C%20and%20the%20second%20about%20why%20he%20did%20it%2C%20then%20the%20third%20asks%20a%20deeper%20question%3A%20what%20made%20him%20do%20it%3F%20This%20time%2C%20the%20setting%20shifts%20to%20a%20children's%20mental-health%20facility%2C%20yet%20another%20institution%20Foucault%20examined.%20A%20space%20designed%20to%20mold%20individuals%2C%20enforce%20conformity%2C%20and%20internalise%20discipline.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20facility%20that%20confine%20Jamie.%20The%20episode%20also%20interrogates%20the%20varied%20forces%20that%20shape%20his%20perceptions%20of%20masculinity%20and%20the%20opposite%20sex.%20The%20media%20he%20consumes%2C%20the%20influences%20he%20absorbs.%20Independent%20psychologist%20Briony%20(a%20terrific%20Erin%20Doherty)%20arrives%20to%20assess%20him.%20Their%20conversation%20begins%20on%20a%20deceptively%20light%20note%2C%20but%20the%20undercurrent%20of%20unease%20is%20quick%20to%20rise.%20Tension%20coils%20tightly%2C%20words%20become%20weapons%2C%20and%20what%20starts%20as%20a%20dialogue%20soon%20fractures%20into%20something%20far%20more%20volatile.%20The%20episode%20unfolds%20almost%20entirely%20within%20a%20single%20room%2C%20yet%20the%20space%20is%20anything%20but%20static.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Uneasy%20Undercurrents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20exchange%20crackles%20with%20complexity.%20There%20are%20shifting%20sympathies%2C%20uneasy%20silences%2C%20unspoken%20truths.%20For%20the%20characters%2C%20the%20spectators%20and%20the%20makers%2C%20it's%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20psychological%20tug-of-war.%20And%20by%20the%20time%20the%20final%20words%20are%20spoken%2C%20the%20show's%20thematic%20core%20stands%20bare%2C%20impossible%20to%20ignore.%20The%20episode%20begins%20with%20Briony%20being%20uneasy%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20an%20old%20guard.%20But%20by%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20really%20Jamie%2C%20a%20teenager%2C%20who%20unsettles%20her.%20His%20gaze%20disturbs%2C%20disarms%2C%20discourages.%20At%20moments%2C%20it%20borders%20on%20an%20assertion%20of%20power%20that%20tilts%20the%20room%20in%20his%20favour.%20This%20ties%20into%20something%20larger%3A%20docility%20entwined%20with%20patriarchy%2C%20the%20way%20women%20are%20conditioned%20to%20internalise%20the%20gaze%2C%20to%20self-discipline%20before%20they%20are%20disciplined.%20A%20body%20that%20resists%2C%20that%20refuses%20to%20be%20subdued%2C%20becomes%20a%20threat%2C%20and%20threats%20are%20often%20erased.%20Perhaps%20that%20is%20why%20the%20victim%2C%20Jamie's%20schoolmate%2C%20is%20never%20seen.%20Perhaps%20that%20is%20why%2C%20at%20a%20breaking%20point%2C%20Frank's%20frustration%20spills%20out%3A%20how%20the%20girl%20will%20be%20forgotten%2C%20how%20the%20story%20will%20always%20be%20about%20Jamie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20Jamie%2C%20the%20creators%20(Jack%20Thorne%2C%20Stephen%20Graham)%20interpret%20docility%20in%20its%20rawest%20form.%20His%20conversations%20with%20Briony%20uncover%20the%20isolation%20and%20bullying%20that%20defined%20his%20school%20life%2C%20showing%20how%20he%20stumbles%20into%20incel%20forums%20and%20the%20manosphere%2C%20where%20resentment%20festers%20and%20power%20is%20promised.%20Andrew%20Tate%20becomes%20his%20guiding%20light%2C%20and%20bit%20by%20bit%2C%20the%20world's%20misogyny%20molds%20him.%20He%20might%20view%20himself%20as%20reclaiming%20masculinity%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20he%20is%20a%20docile%20body%2C%20subservient%20to%20the%20same%20heteronormative%2C%20misogynistic%20structures%20that%20claim%20to%20liberate%20him.%20And%20as%20Foucault%20argued%20long%20before%20this%20age%20of%20screens%2C%20technology%20only%20tightens%20the%20grip.%20The%20panopticon%20no%20longer%20needs%20prison%20walls.%20Now%20it%20thrives%20in%20algorithms%2C%20in%20likes%20and%20comments%20that%20surveil%20and%20shape%20without%20presence.%20Behavior%20shifts.%20Patterns%20form.%20Not%20because%20we%20are%20seen%2C%20but%20because%20we%20might%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%20As%20A%20Prison%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20this%20idea%20of%20watchfulness%20that%20begins%20to%20unsettle%20Jamie's%20parents%20in%20the%20final%20episode%2C%20which%20is%20also%20the%20most%20subversive%20and%20gut-wrenching%20of%20the%20lot.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20institution%20under%20scrutiny%20is%20not%20a%20school%2C%20a%20police%20station%2C%20or%20a%20mental-health%20facility.%20It%20is%20a%20home.%20And%20at%20its%20centre%20stands%20a%20family%2C%20crumbling%20under%20the%20burden%20of%20what%20they%20failed%20to%20see.%20We%20see%20Eddie%20(a%20devastating%20Stephen%20Graham)%20seething%20with%20rage%2C%20his%20fear%20spilling%20over%20into%20violence.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20uncontrollable%20outrage%2C%20he%20nearly%20harms%20two%20teenagers.%20His%20voice%20echoes%20through%20the%20house%2C%20his%20shouts%20filling%20the%20air.%20He%20storms%20through%20rooms%2C%20arguing%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20clutching%20desperately%20at%20the%20illusion%20of%20protecting%20his%20daughter.%20But%20as%20the%20walls%20close%20in%2C%20a%20question%20remains%3A%20how%20much%20of%20Jamie's%20violence%20was%20inherited%3F%20Did%20his%20father's%20anger%2C%20his%20unchecked%20masculinity%2C%20seep%20into%20him%20like%20a%20second%20skin%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fgws%2Fms%2Floved-adolescence-watch-these-crime-dramas-next%2Fassets%2F5.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20Eddie%20wonders%20the%20same.%20In%20the%20closing%20moments%2C%20he%20breaks%20down%2C%20consumed%20by%20the%20unbearable%20thought%3A%20where%20did%20I%20go%20wrong%3F%20His%20wife%2C%20in%20her%20own%20disbelief%2C%20wrestles%20with%20another%20question%3A%20how%20was%20Jamie%20always%20there%2C%20just%20across%20the%20room%2C%20yet%20so%20distant%3F%20Was%20it%20that%20they%20didn't%20watch%20him%20closely%20enough%3F%20Or%20perhaps%2C%20in%20his%20desperation%20not%20to%20become%20like%20his%20own%20father%2C%20Eddie%20became%20something%20else%20entirely.%20A%20fa