ndia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsamantha-ruth-prabhu-is-the-only-celeb-who-rejected-rs-200-crore-alimony-after-her-divorce-with-naga-chaitanya-report%2Farticleshow%2F119371057.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20US%20Attorney%2C%20Who%20Quit%20After%20Trump%20Took%20Office%2C%20Found%20Dead%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJessica%20Aber%2C%20the%20former%20US%20Attorney%20for%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20Virginia%20(EDVA)%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20her%20home%20on%20Saturday%2C%20officials%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%2043-year-old%20lawyer%2C%20who%20resigned%20after%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20took%20office%20in%20January%2C%20was%20discovered%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Virginia's%20Alexandria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20is%20underway%20surrounding%20the%20circumstances%20of%20her%20death%2C%20the%20police%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20morning%2C%20at%20approximately%209%3A18%20am%2C%20Alexandria%20Police%20responded%20to%20the%20900%20block%20of%20Beverley%20Drive%20for%20the%20report%20of%20an%20unresponsive%20woman.%20Officers%20located%20a%20deceased%20woman%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Medical%20Examiner%20of%20Virginia%20will%20determine%20the%20cause%20and%20manner%20of%20death%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incumbent%20US%20Attorney%20for%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20Virginia%2C%20Erik%20S%20Siebert%2C%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bheartbroken%20beyond%20words%26quot%3B%20to%20learn%20about%20Ms%20Aber's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20unmatched%20as%20a%20leader%2C%20mentor%2C%20and%20prosecutor%2C%20and%20she%20is%20simply%20irreplaceable%20as%20a%20human%20being.%20We%20remain%20in%20awe%20of%20how%20much%20she%20accomplished%20in%20her%20all%20too%20brief%20time%20in%20this%20world.%20Her%20professionalism%2C%20grace%2C%20and%20legal%20acumen%20set%20the%20standard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20we%20are%20devastated%20by%20this%20loss%2C%20each%20of%20us%20in%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20Virginia%20will%20look%20to%20her%20example%20and%20endeavor%20to%20live%20up%20to%20that%20standard.%20Jess%20was%20a%20proud%20Virginian%20from%20high%20school%20through%20college%20and%20throughout%20her%20career.%20She%20loved%20EDVA%20and%20EDVA%20loved%20her%20back.%20%C2%A0We%20remain%20committed%20to%20her%20life's%20work%2C%20a%20commitment%20to%20seeking%20justice%2C%20as%20she%20would%20have%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Was%20Jessica%20Aber%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJessica%20Aber%20was%20nominated%20as%20the%20United%20States%20Attorney%20for%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20Virginia%20by%20then%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20August%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20began%20her%20service%20in%20the%20EDVA%20in%202009%20as%20an%20Assistant%20US%20Attorney%2C%20prosecuting%20financial%20fraud%2C%20public%20corruption%2C%20violent%20crime%2C%20and%20child%20exploitation%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202015%20to%202016%2C%20Ms%20Aber%20served%20on%20a%20detailed%20assignment%20as%20counsel%20to%20the%20Assistant%20Attorney%20General%20for%20the%20Criminal%20Division%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%20From%202016%20until%20becoming%20US%20Attorney%2C%20she%20also%20served%20as%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Division%20for%20EDVA.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742716020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F4scr5ef_jessica-aber_625x300_23_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjessica-aber-former-us-attorney-who-quit-after-donald-trump-took-office-found-dead-at-home-7990202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jessica%20Aber%20was%20nominated%20as%20the%20United%20States%20Attorney%20for%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20Virginia%20by%20Joe%20Biden%20in%202021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Elon%20Musk's%20Trans%20Daughter%20Snubbed%20X%20For%20Rivals%20Bluesky%2C%20Threads%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVivian%20Jenna%20Wilson%2C%20the%2020-year-old%20estranged%20daughter%20of%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20she%20wants%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20her%20father-%20or%20his%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20Instead%2C%20she%20has%20found%20a%20digital%20home%20on%20rival%20platforms%20like%20Meta's%20Threads%20and%C2%A0Bluesky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Vivian%20Wilson%20Is%20Not%20On%20Elon%20Musk-Owned%20X%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivian%20Wilson%20has%20been%20highly%20active%20on%20Meta's%20Threads%20and%20Bluesky%2C%20a%20decentralised%20social%20media%20platform%20that%20many%20see%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20Elon%20Musk's%20X.%20Musk%20acquired%20Twitter%20(now%20X)%20in%202022%20-%20the%20same%20year%20Wilson%20legally%20changed%20her%20name%2C%20writing%20in%20a%20petition%20that%20she%20no%20longer%20wished%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Brelated%20to%20%5Bher%5D%20biological%20father%20in%20any%20way%2C%20shape%2C%20or%20form.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teenvogue.com%2Fstory%2Fvivian-jenna-wilson-elon-musk-trans-youth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETeen%20Vogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20interview%2C%20she%20also%20confirmed%20that%20she%20is%20financially%20independent%20from%20him%20and%20has%20no%20desire%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBluesky%2C%20originally%20launched%20as%20a%20side%20project%20by%20Twitter's%20co-founder%20Jack%20Dorsey%20in%202019%2C%20gained%20traction%20after%20Musk's%20takeover.%20Many%20users%2C%20frustrated%20by%20his%20approach%20to%20content%20moderation%2C%20flocked%20to%20the%20platform.%20Now%20with%20over%2028%20million%20users%2C%20Bluesky%20has%20become%20a%20refuge%20for%20those%20seeking%20a%20less%20politically%20charged%20social%20media%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EVivian%20Wilson's%20Relationship%20With%20father%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilson%20has%20distanced%20herself%20from%20Musk%20for%20years%2C%20particularly%20after%20coming%20out%20as%20transgender%20in%202020.%20Musk%20has%20continued%20to%20speak%20about%20her%20publicly.%20In%20a%202024%20interview%20with%20manosphere%20influencer%20Jordan%20Peterson%2C%20Musk%20repeatedly%20deadnamed%20Wilson%20and%20claimed%20she%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bkilled%20by%20the%20woke%20mind%20virus.%26quot%3B%20His%20remarks%20echoed%20how%20she%20was%20portrayed%20in%20Walter%20Isaacson's%20biography%20of%20Musk%20-%20as%20an%20angry%2C%20rebellious%20child%20with%20radical%20political%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivian%20Wilson%20responded%20on%20Meta's%20Threads%2C%20calling%20Musk's%20portrayal%20of%20her%20%26quot%3Bentirely%20fake%26quot%3B%20and%20accusing%20him%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bdesperate%20for%20attention%20and%20validation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EVivian%20Wilson%2C%20The%20'Queen%20of%20Threads'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivian%20Wilson%20calls%20herself%20the%20%26quot%3BQueen%20of%20Threads%26quot%3B%20and%20frequently%20posts%20on%20Threads%2C%20Bluesky%2C%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram.%20She%20even%20%26quot%3Bratioed%26quot%3B%20Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20on%20Threads%2C%20an%20achievement%20she%20described%20as%20making%20her%20feel%20like%20%26quot%3Bthe%20f**king%20queen.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20Queen%20of%20Threads%3B%20that's%20my%20branding%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Teen%20Vogue.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20Bluesky%2C%20but%20'Queen%20of%20Bluesky'%20doesn't%20have%20the%20same%20ring%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHer%20Take%20on%20Social%20Media%20and%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vivian%20Wilson%20acknowledges%20social%20media's%20power%20in%20raising%20awareness%2C%20she%20is%20also%20wary%20of%20its%20dangers%20-%20particularly%20the%20rise%20of%20online%20radicalisation%20through%20spaces%20like%204chan.%20She%20pointed%20to%20the%20role%20social%20media%20played%20in%20bringing%20attention%20to%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20initially%20found%20out%20about%20that%20issue%20from%20social%20media.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20asked%20to%20verify%20social%20media%20information%20rather%20than%20blindly%20trusting%20online%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20she%20doesn't%20see%20herself%20as%20a%20political%20activist%2C%20Wilson%20feels%20a%20strong%20obligation%20to%20speak%20out%20on%20trans%20rights%2C%20particularly%20in%20defence%20of%20minors%20receiving%20gender-affirming%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHer%20Thoughts%20on%20Right-Wing%20Social%20Media%20Users%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivian%20Wilson%20calls%20right-wing%20social%20media%20influencers%20%26quot%3Bbad%20at%20posting%26quot%3B%20and%20lacking%20charisma.%20She%20argues%20that%20humour%20is%20essential%20for%20engaging%20audiences%20and%20that%20many%20conservative%20figures%20fail%20to%20be%20entertaining.%20Despite%20this%2C%20she%20acknowledges%20that%20right-wing%20users%20dominate%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20X%20and%20Meta%2C%20though%20she%20finds%20it%20puzzling%20given%20what%20she%20sees%20as%20their%20lack%20of%20posting%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20her%20own%20social%20media%20skills%2C%20Vivian%20Wilson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20I'm%20good%20at%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Teen%20Vogue.%20%26quot%3BI%20make%20posts.%20Sometimes%20peopl