th%20the%20Rapido%20captain%20on%20her%20%26quot%3BKali%20(black)%20Activa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20best%20decision%20ever%20because%20she%20was%20absolutely%20entertaining.%20Such%20a%20jolly%20person!%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sahu%20wrote.%20What%20truly%20touched%20her%20was%20Ms%20Tripathi's%20inspiring%20life%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rapido%20captain%2C%20apart%20from%20ferrying%20passengers%2C%20is%20also%20a%20chef%20by%20profession.%20She%20joined%20the%20ride-hailing%20platform%20simply%20because%20she%20enjoys%20riding%20her%20scooter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sahu%20recalled%20how%20Ms%20Tripathi%20frequently%20checked%20in%20on%20her%20comfort%20with%20questions%20like%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMa'am%2C%20zyada%20tez%20toh%20nahi%20chala%20rahi%20na%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(Am%20I%20riding%20too%20fast%3F)%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAap%20aaram%20se%20toh%20baithe%20ho%20na%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(Are%20you%20seated%20comfortably%3F).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20wasn't%20just%20talking%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it%2C%20I%20could%20tell%20she%20had%20been%20through%20some%20tough%20times%20simply%20by%20the%20way%20she%20appreciated%20every%20little%20happy%20moment%20in%20her%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sahu%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%2035-minute%20ride%20flew%20by%20in%20an%20instant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20Ms%20Tripathi's%20details%20in%20a%20screenshot%20which%20showed%20her%20in%20a%20chef%20uniform.%20%26quot%3BBelow%20are%20her%20details%2C%20in%20case%20Rapido%20decides%20to%20reward%20her%20in%20any%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sahu%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7308531629906374657%3Fcollapsed%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20soon%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20so%20cool.%20Good%20vibes%20only.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BWow%2C%20such%20a%20superb%20and%20beautiful%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20someone%20who%20is%20scared%20to%20book%20rides%20on%20uber%20or%20ola%20anymore%2C%20this%20makes%20me%20so%20much%20happier%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20comment%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomeone%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20a%20wholesome%20moment!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Rapido%20co-founder%20Pavan%20Guntupalli%20announced%20that%20the%20company%20would%20launch%20its%20women-only%20bike%20taxi%20service%20called%20'Bike%20Pink'%20in%20Karnataka.%20It%20would%20create%2025%2C000%20jobs%20for%20women.%20The%20service%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%20Chennai%20in%20September%202024.%20They%20also%20plan%20to%20expand%20'Bike%20Pink'%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742710860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-02%2Fjai47muc_rapido-bike-taxi-in-lucknow_625x300_11_February_19.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbest-decision-why-delhi-woman-cancelled-uber-cab-for-female-rapido-captain-7989404%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Delhi%20woman's%20ride%20with%20Rapido%20turned%20into%20an%20unexpectedly%20%26quot%3Bwholesome%20experience%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20met%20a%20female%20captain%20who%20was%20also%20a%20chef.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbest-decision-why-delhi-woman-cancelled-uber-cab-for-female-rapido-captain-7989404%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gurugram%20Cops%20Slap%20Rs%201%2C000%20Fine%20On%20Drunk%20Man%20In%20Car.%20He%20Wasn't%20Driving%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Gurugram%20man%20was%20allegedly%20fined%20Rs%201%2C000%20by%20the%20police%20for%20being%